{"tid":1914264,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"（全新）金牛jj吹水活動感情tg谷","createTime":"2020-03-07T12:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T16:37:30.000Z","uid":217514,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"328c99e6f7fca90ccc6e2fd35c673e3994ec9739","tid":1914264,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">個谷等齊人就開 包保全新㗎</span><br />\n《性格保守且沈穩的金牛座男生，如同歸隱詩人般追求安穩恬靜的田園生活。》<br />\n《八面玲瓏的金牛座女生，恰到好處的交際手腕總能贏得眾人的好感。》<br />\n<br />\n金牛座不嬲都唔係好多人理解到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身為金牛座嘅你嚟圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然大家都未必係星座撚 但主要想搵返同星座嘅人嚟吹水<br />\n仲可以搞下生日聚添<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然都歡迎想溝金牛座仔仔/女女嘅你嚟問下各位大師如何入手<br />\n<br />\n依個谷乜都吹得 唔歡迎藍絲呀！明㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n活動都會搞 想乜聚有乜聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對狗公娘娘表示強烈不了 你做咩都會有人知㗎<br />\n當然你要扮你喺金牛都唔緊要 只係無乜意思～<br />\n其他星座jj有意入嚟分享你嘅故事求救好歡迎㗎！<br />\n<br />\n間唔時會清人 有意入嚟就填form<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/zMSUkKpQgU9UCtgb9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FzMSUkKpQgU9UCtgb9&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=6369b126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/zMSUkKpQgU9UCtgb9</a>"},{"pid":"08ab8306b2974d2511a8ffda6a00b44212ac57cc","tid":1914264,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d62b78786513959e6cf7db6f636dd29ec9694c","tid":1914264,"uid":9984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"填左2次都未入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4a27d840abdaa86b3cf256cf2cb43a9aa5b843","tid":1914264,"uid":217514,"like":0,"dislike":